\color inherit
：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
t_{\mathrm{br}}(\varOmega)\coloneqq\inf_{p_{0},q_{0}}\left\{ t_{*}(p_{0},q_{0})\mid(p_{0},q_{0})\in\varOmega\times\varOmega,\ p_{0}<q_{0}\right\} 
