\begin_inset Formula $t_{\mathrm{br}}$
\end_inset

 的值。考虑到光滑解破裂的实质是
\color blue
函数值发生跳跃
\color inherit
，这意味着 
\begin_inset Formula $\pdv*{u}{x}\to\infty$
\end_inset

，于是寻找 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{\mathrm{br}}$
\end_inset

 的问题就转化为寻找 
\begin_inset Formula $\pdv*{u}{x}\to\infty$
\end_inset

 的条件。为此，先用
\color blue
隐函数求导法则
\color inherit
计算光滑解的偏导数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pdv{u(x,t)}{x}=\left(1-\dv{a(u)}{u}\pdv{u(x,t)}{x}\left(x-x_{0}\right)\right)\dv{u_{0}}{x_{0}}
\]

\end_inset

再用 
\begin_inset Formula $u(x,t)=u_{0}(x_{0})$
\end_inset

 及链式求导法则 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：单波：链式求导"

\end_inset

 可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pdv{u(x,t)}{x}=\frac{\dv*{u_{0}}{x_{0}}}{1+(t-t_{0})\dv*{a}{x_{0}}}
\]

\end_inset

若等式右端的分母为零，则有 
\begin_inset Formula $\pdv*{u}{x}\to\infty$
\end_inset

，此即光滑解破裂的（充分）条件：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
t_{\mathrm{br}}(x_{0})=t_{0}-\left(\dv*{a}{x_{0}}\right)^{-1}
\]

\end_inset

这是始于点 
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},t_{0})$
\end_inset

