\begin_inset Formula $\varOmega$
\end_inset

 的）光滑解的破裂时刻
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{t_{\mathrm{br}}(\varOmega)=\inf_{x_{0}\in\varOmega}\left\{ t_{0}-\left(\dv*{a}{x_{0}}\right)^{-1}\right\} }
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

