\begin_layout Subsection
高阶线性方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Problem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[无限长弹性弦]
\end_layout

\end_inset

一维无限长均匀弹性弦的横向微幅振动是由
\color blue
二阶线性波动方程
\color inherit
描述的：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}-a^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial x^{2}}\right)u=0\qquad(x,t)\in(-\infty,\infty)\times(0,\infty)\label{eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

相应的初始条件由
\color blue
初始位移
\color inherit
和
\color blue
初始速度
\color inherit
共同构成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u(x,t=0)=u_{0}(x)\qquad\frac{\partial u(x,t=0)}{\partial t}=v_{0}(x)\label{eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波：初值}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 中的二阶微分算符可以分解为两个一阶微分算符的
\color blue
乘积
\color inherit
：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}-a^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial x^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}-a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)
\]

\end_inset

引入坐标变换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\xi\\
\eta
\end{bmatrix}\coloneqq\begin{bmatrix}x+at\\
x-at
\end{bmatrix}\implies\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\xi & \partial_{t}\eta\\
\partial_{x}\xi & \partial_{x}\eta
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}a & -a\\
1 & 1
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

只要该变换是非退化的，即 
\begin_inset Formula $a\ne0$
\end_inset

，就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}-a\partial_{x}\\
\partial_{t}+a\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & -a\\
1 & +a
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix} & -2a\\
2a
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

于是可以将方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 化为
\color blue
标准形式 (canonical form)
\color inherit
：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\xi}\partial_{\eta}u=0
\]

\end_inset

它的通解为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,t)=f(\xi)+g(\eta)=f(x+at)+g(x-at)
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 可以是任何一阶可微的一元函数。代入初始条件 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波：初值"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 可以定出 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

，从而得到原初值问题的解：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,t)=\frac{u_{0}(x+at)+u_{0}(x-at)}{2}+\int_{x-at}^{x+at}\frac{v_{0}(\zeta)}{2a}\dd{\zeta}
\]

\end_inset

它表示两个独立的（线性）波分别以速度 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm a$
\end_inset

 沿 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 方向运动。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[矩阵记法]
\end_layout

\end_inset

若将一阶导数分别视作独立的未知函数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U_{1}\coloneqq\frac{\partial u}{\partial t}\qquad U_{2}\coloneqq\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}
\]

\end_inset

则二阶偏微分方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 及二阶交叉导数的协调条件 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}\partial_{x}u=\partial_{x}\partial_{t}u$
\end_inset

 可以化为一阶偏微分方程组：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t} & -a^{2}\partial_{x}\\
-\partial_{x} & \partial_{t}
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}U_{1}\\
U_{2}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}0\\
0
\end{bmatrix}\qquad\begin{bmatrix}U_{1}(x,t=0)\\
U_{2}(x,t=0)
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}v_{0}(x)\\
\dd{u_{0}(x)}/\dd{x}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

本章剩余部分都将讨论这种（关于整数个未知函数的）方程组。
\end_layout

