\alpha_{1-}=u_{-}-a_{-}\qquad\alpha_{1+}=u_{*}-\cancelto{0}{a_{*}}=u_{*}+\frac{2\cancelto{0}{a_{*}}}{\gamma-1}=u_{-}+\frac{2a_{-}}{\gamma-1}
\]

