 为右行膨胀波，波头波尾速度分别为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\alpha_{3+}=u_{+}+a_{+}\qquad\alpha_{3-}=u_{*}+\cancelto{0}{a_{*}}=u_{*}-\frac{2\cancelto{0}{a_{*}}}{\gamma-1}=u_{+}-\frac{2a_{+}}{\gamma-1}
\]

